flavor_text: This Pokemon fought humans in order to protect its friends. Legends about it continue to be passed down.
Its head sprouts horns as sharp as blades. Using whirlwind-like movements it confounds and swiftly cuts opponents.
Legends say this Pokemon confounded opponents with its swift movements.
